===============================
=========== INTENTS ===========
===============================

1. What are intents?
-- Used for starting various tasks on the phone
-- Main Activity is the default intent

2. Types of intents
-- Start an activity
-- Start a background service
-- Broadcast (to other apps)

3. Explicit vs. Implicit intents
-- Explicit intents know what app/component to use (typically within own app)
-- Implicit intents do not name the executing app
---- Useful within the eco-system
---- Activity choosers

4. Passing data
-- Extra Data
-- StartActivityForResult & onActivityResult

5. Intent filters
-- Categories, who might resolve this?
-- Actions, what are we doing?
-- Allow start from other apps

6. Code example
